# - Try to find Log4C
# Once done this will define
#
#  LOG4C_FOUND - system has Log4C
#  LOG4C_INCLUDE_DIRS - the Log4C include directory
#  LOG4C_LIBRARIES - Link these to use Log4C
#  LOG4C_DEFINITIONS - Compiler switches required for using Log4C
